name: Salmon Patties
author: Anonymous
summary: Bisquick Heart Smart® recipe! Fishing for a twist on burgers? You’ve found it!
ingredients: ½ cup Bisquick Heart Smart® mix
1 (14.75 ounce) can red salmon, skin and bone removed, drained and flaked
4 each whole wheat burger buns, split
4 tablespoons dill dip or Ranch dip
directions: In medium bowl, mix all ingredients except margarine, buns, lettuce and dill dip
Shape mixture into 4 patties, using heaping 1/2 cupfuls for each patty
In 10-inch nonstick skillet, melt margarine over medium heat
Cook patties in margarine over medium heat 10 to 12 minutes, turning once, until brown and cooked through
Fill buns with lettuce, salmon patties and dill dip
